        "jsCode": "// Loop over input items and add a new field called 'myNewField' to the JSON of each one\nconst contents = $input.all().map(item => item.json.content).filter(Boolean);\nconst context = contents.join(\"\\n\\n\");\nreturn [{ json: { context } }];"
      },
